270
00:24:23,220 --> 00:24:24,440
Xuan Xuan!

271
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:26,440
- Xuan Xuan!
- Xuan Xuan!

272
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:29,150
- Xuan Xuan!
- Xuan Xuan!

273
00:24:29,150 --> 00:24:32,130
