323
00:27:20,310 --> 00:27:24,680
Where's your watch? Call Mommy.

324
00:27:25,390 --> 00:27:29,700
No battery. What do we do now?

325
00:27:29,700 --> 00:27:31,240
I don't know.

326
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:35,780
