347
00:29:25,070 --> 00:29:29,150
Brother, I miss daddy.

348
00:29:29,150 --> 00:29:31,670
I also miss mommy.

349
00:29:31,670 --> 00:29:35,760
Let's find a policeman uncle to take us home.

350
00:29:35,760 --> 00:29:39,540
